.TH LPF-KERNEL-MATRIX 8 "June 2026" "lpf 0.1.0-dev" "lpf Manual"
.SH NAME
lpf\-kernel\-matrix \- run or plan latest\-kernel validation
.SH SYNOPSIS
lpf kernel\-matrix <plan|run>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Plan or run latest\-five kernel compatibility validation.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\-\-lab <id>
select a lab profile such as 141
.SH EXAMPLES
lpf kernel\-matrix plan
lpf kernel\-matrix run \-\-lab 141
.SH FILES
/var/lib/lpf/kernel\-matrix
.SH SAFETY NOTES
Do not commit raw lab logs, credentials, private inventories, or secret material.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success.
Non\-zero when validation, planning, or host operations fail.
.SH SEE ALSO
lpf\-support\-bundle(8)
